  "prompt": "How many credits are on Quora?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Quora used a system of credits that allowed users to ask questions and promote content. The exact number of credits available to users can vary based on a number of factors, including activity on the platform and specific promotions that Quora might be running. Users typically earn credits by participating in the community, such as by asking questions or providing answers.\n\nTo get the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding Quora credits, it's best to check directly on the Quora platform or consult their help page, as policies and systems may have changed after my last update.",
